Package: owidR
Type: Package
Title: A package for getting data from Our World in Data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Piers York
Maintainer: Piers York <piersyork+owidr@gmail.com>
Description: Scrapes data from the Our World in Data github repo to offer easy to use functions for searching for datasets and downloading them into R.
